descriptionNullable: Dataset of The Onion satirical news. Scraped from https://www.theonion.com/breaking-news/news-in-brief. The data includes the title of the news, the time of publication, and the detailed content. This dataset can be used as a complementary corpus for NLP tasks such as satirical text classification / fake news classification.
title: Satirical News from The Onion
